comments: Plumlee (CHA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Reaves (LAL) and does not deliver contact.
Plumlee (CHA) makes marginal contact with Reaves (LAL) as he establishes post position.
Rozier (CHA) moves into Westbrook (LAL) and makes body contact that affects his SQBR.
Plumlee (CHA) makes incidental contact with Davis (LAL) with a collapsed arm as he drives to the basket.
Davis (LAL) brings his arms forward, but the contact with Plumlee's (CHA) off-arm during the shot attempt is marginal.
Bridges (CHA) moves along with Bradley (LAL) on his path to the basket and the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Davis (LAL) jumps to contest the jump shot by Rozier (CHA) and lands ahead of him without making contact.  The contact after Rozier returns to the floor is marginal.
Reaves (LAL) legally contests Bridges' (CHA) jump shot attempt.
Bridges (CHA) legally contests Davis's (LAL) jump shot attempt.
Ball (CHA) places his arm against Reaves (LAL), who is moving in the opposite direction of the ball, and Reaves loses his balance when the two players make incidental foot contact.
The timeout by the Hornets is recognized before any possible foul on Westbrook (LAL).
Westbrook (LAL) makes marginal contact with Hayward (CHA) before cleanly dislodging the ball during his drive.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Replay review of the out-of-bounds call off of Hayward (CHA) pursuant to a coach's challenge is deemed unsuccessful.  The ball is last touched by Hayward before going out of bounds.
Westbrook (LAL) trips Ball (CHA), affecting his SQBR.
Plumlee (CHA) makes contact to Davis's (LAL) arm, affecting his dunk attempt.
Rozier (CHA) makes incidental contact with Westbrook (LAL) during the rebound.
Davis (LAL) cleanly blocks the jump shot attempt by Rozier (CHA) and any contact to his hand and body after the block is incidental.
Anthony (LAL) legally contests Martin's (CHA) jump shot attempt.
